ccessibility Standards',\n   210→      body: 'Web accessibility ensures websites are usable by people with disabilities. Follow WCAG guidelines: provide alt text for images, ensure keyboard navigation, use semantic HTML, maintain sufficient color contrast, add ARIA labels, and test with screen readers. Accessibility benefits all users.',\n   211→      tags: JSON.stringify(['programming', 'web', 'accessibility']),\n   212→    },\n   213→    {\n   214→      title: 'Italian Risotto Masterclass',\n   215→      body: 'Perfect risotto requires Arborio or Carnaroli rice, warm stock, patience, and constant stirring. Toast the rice in butter, add wine, then ladle warm stock gradually while stirring. The starch releases slowly, creating a creamy texture. Finish with butter and Parmigiano-Reggiano.',\n   216→      tags: JSON.stringify(['cooking', 'italian', 'recipes']),\n   217→    },\n   218→    {\n   219→      title: 'Artificial Neural Networks Explained',\n   220→      body: 'Neural networks are computing systems inspired by biological neural networks. They consist of layers of interconnected nodes (neurons) that process information. Deep learning uses many hidden layers to learn hierarchical representations. Applications include image recognition, natural language processing, and autonomous vehicles.',\n   221→      tags: JSON.stringify(['programming', 'ai', 'deep-learning']),\n   222→    },\n   223→    {\n   224→      title: 'Sustainable Living Tips',\n   225→      body: 'Reduce your environmental footprint by minimizing single-use plastics, composting food waste, choosing renewable energy, buying local produce, reducing water usage, and using public transport or cycling. Small daily choices collectively make a significant environmental impact.',\n   226→      tags: JSON.stringify(['environment', 'lifestyle', 'sustainability']),\n   227→    },\n   228→    {\n   229→      title: 'Chess Strategy for Intermediates',\n   230→      body: 'Improve your chess by studying opening